name: log_with_base_in_map
description:
Returns the logarithm of a value to a base. The input can be any numeric value, the return value is always a double.

Logs of zero, negative numbers, and base of one return `null` as well as a warning.

params.name: number
params.description: Numeric expression. If `null`, the function returns `null`.

params.description: Input value. The input is a valid constant map expression.
